{
  "description": "A nighttime view of a city skyline illuminated by numerous lights, featuring a prominent bridge and a vibrant fireworks display. The bridge, likely the Bay Bridge, extends horizontally across the dark waters, its towers and cables clearly visible.  Fireworks explode above a tall building in the city center, creating bursts of red, white, and blue light. The cityscape itself is densely packed with buildings of varying heights, all aglow with lights.  The dark waters below reflect the city lights, and distant hills or mountains are visible on the horizon. The overall composition is a long, wide shot emphasizing the scale and grandeur of the urban landscape and the celebratory fireworks.",
